<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风停了。悟空跳起来叫回了那些小悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。”八戒抱怨着说，“我得睡一觉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“起来！”悟空大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得在妖怪吃了师父之前把他救回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒抓了抓脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么才能把他救回来呢？那风实在太强了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摸着下巴想了想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我偷偷进洞里去看看能发现点什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变成了一只蚊子，从洞门的一条裂缝里进去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在洞穴深处，他听到有人在哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是师父的声音。”悟空想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空发现他的师父被绑在一个很黑的房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父！”悟空大叫。他落在了唐僧的肩膀上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是悟空吗？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他四处看了看：“你在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在你肩膀上。”悟空说，“我把自己变成了一只蚊子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定要救我出去。”唐僧说。他又开始哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别哭了。”悟空说，“你很快就会自由了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先我必须打败那妖怪。我会回来的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空沿着隧道向下飞去，最后到了正殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄风怪正在和其他的妖怪说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您的吹风术把孙悟空吹跑了。”一个妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄风怪大笑。“只有灵吉菩萨可以挡住我的吹风术。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>点火！我们今晚要大吃一顿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！”悟空想，“灵吉菩萨就住在须弥山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我去找他帮忙，现在就去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到云上，在天上快速飞行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他到达须弥山的时候，灵吉菩萨正从他的宝塔里出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很高兴见到你，悟空。”灵吉菩萨说，“要喝点茶吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不了，谢谢。”悟空说，“我有件急事！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他迅速把发生的所有事情都告诉了灵吉菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我试过和那妖怪斗，”悟空说，“但他用了厉害的吹风术。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道黄风怪是谁。”灵吉菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是只貂鼠。佛祖叫我盯着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我告诉过那妖怪，如果他老实，就可以住在那座山上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灵吉菩萨摇摇头：“看来他开始做坏事了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能帮帮我吗？”悟空问，“他们今晚就要吃了唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”灵吉菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿了飞龙宝杖，又把一个小东西放在了自己的袈裟里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他们就飞上了天，他们向下看着洞门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去敲门吧。”灵吉菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让那妖怪出来，剩下的事情我来做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空降到了洞门前，拿出了他的金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哗啦！洞门碎成了一片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄风怪冲了出来大叫：“你砸坏了我的洞门！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277627</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大口的吹了三口气，但什么事情都没发生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么回事？”黄风怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头看到了天上的灵吉菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灵吉菩萨的手里拿着一颗宝珠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“定风珠！”黄风怪大叫，然后就跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灵吉菩萨把他的飞龙宝杖扔了下来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>飞龙宝杖变成了一条金龙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金龙把黄风怪扔到了石头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵烟雾散去后，那妖怪变成了一只黄色的貂鼠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灵吉菩萨拿起了貂鼠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会带它去佛祖面前受罚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空，你可以去找你的师父了。祝你好运！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跑到了洞里赶走了其他妖怪，然后他解开了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们二人又走了出来，结果发现八戒在睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>361119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>366989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“醒醒，呆子！”悟空叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>